            "html": "<p class=\"q-text qu-display--block qu-wordBreak--break-word qu-textAlign--start\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">Maybe. It could be nice on long trips, but I enjoy driving and don't know if I would like giving up the control. It is a major trust issue. I know computers fail, lock up, get corrupted, get hacked, and software designers cannot think of every scenario. People will die, accidents will happen,and as long as I feel more confident in my skills, I will keep driving.</span></p>",
